description:
The PMD Java 8 parse (which is used in the class `JavaSourceDependencyCollector`) fails on code like that:

``` java
object.event = () -> {
    Request request = new Request();
    request.id = 42;
};
```

The bug is reported to the PMD guys as [#1258 Java 8 Lambda parse error on direct field access ](http://sourceforge.net/p/pmd/bugs/1258/).

